{{Top|real}}
The '''Lucasfilm Archives''' is a large facility located at [[Skywalker Ranch]] designed to preserve and document items from Lucasfilm productions. Currently, the archives contain elements from the ''[[Star Wars]]'' films, the ''[[Indiana Jones]]'' films, [[Willow (film)|''Willow'']], [[Wikipedia:American Graffiti|''American Graffiti'']], and [[Wikipedia:Tucker: The Man and His Dream|''Tucker: The Man and His Dream'']]. All elements are carefully kept under climate control.

